snippet.title: Poncho - EGX Rezzed Exclusive Trailer
snippet.description:
A Platformer like nothing seen before, explore this open-world puzzler in multiple dimensions on a journey to find your Maker. 

Coming soon to STEAM, PS4, PSVita and Wii U!

http://poncho-game.com/
